number of cycles per unit time.

00:07:06.220 --> 00:07:11.680
So we talk about wavelength,
amplitude, and frequency.

00:07:11.680 --> 00:07:14.370
And as you turn the
page, we can also

00:07:14.370 --> 00:07:17.610
