00:19:18.130 --> 00:19:21.120
And one of the most
important properties of waves

00:19:21.120 --> 00:19:24.330
is that they can superimpose.

00:19:24.330 --> 00:19:28.020
So if you have two
waves, one drawn up here,

00:19:28.020 --> 00:19:32.650
